# ─── Harness Agent — Development Repo ──────────────────────────────────────────
# This is the harness development repository. ALL harness files are tracked here.
# .sessions/, knowledge/index_*.json, harness_flow_*.md → all committed.
#
# When deploying harness to a TARGET PROJECT:
#   → Use Implement/03_config.md §Gitignore to add harness runtime exclusions
#   → Use scripts/bootstrap_sessions.py to initialize .sessions/ on first run
#   → Templates: docs/session_templates/

# ─── macOS resource forks ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
._*
.DS_Store

# ─── Claude Code local settings ────────────────────────────────────────────────
.claude/settings.local.json

# ─── Transient per-task scratch (T-230b) ──────────────────────────────────────
# Scope-baseline snapshot — regenerated every task by scripts/posttool_track.py
# when gather_complete.md is written. Must stay untracked so it never appears in
# its own `git status --porcelain` snapshot (would self-flag the [scope-creep] gate).
.sessions/.scope_baseline

# ─── Python ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
